# 3. Deployment Architecture

System architecture:

Telegram ↓ Telegram Bot (aiogram) ↓ Backend API (FastAPI) ↓ Redis Queue
↓ Workers (future) ↓ PostgreSQL

All services run as Docker containers on the VPS.

Docker containers:

ai_bot ai_backend ai_redis ai_postgres

Managed through:

